  "body": "Hi! I have a documentation issue on InstantSearch.js. I could not find what I was looking for on the page \"[connectCurrentRefinedValues](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/connectors/connectCurrentRefinedValues.html)\".\r\n\r\n<!-- Describe what you're looking for here. -->\r\n\r\nthe example code is not working:\r\n\"Uncaught TypeError: CurrentRefinedValuesRenderingOptions.find is not a function\"\r\n\r\nIn the lines: \"CurrentRefinedValuesRenderingOptions.find('ul').html(list);\" and the below one must replace \"CurrentRefinedValuesRenderingOptions\" with \"containerNode\"\r\nso it become:\r\n\"CurrentRefinedValuesRenderingOptions.find('ul').html(list);\"\r\nand\r\n\"CurrentRefinedValuesRenderingOptions.find('li > a').each(function(index) {...\"",
